NAME
     ilogb, ilogbf, ilogbl -- extract exponent

LIBRARY
     Math Library (libm, -lm)

SYNOPSIS
     #include <math.h>

     int
     ilogb(double x);

     int
     ilogbf(float x);

     int
     ilogbl(long double x);

DESCRIPTION
     iillooggbb(), iillooggbbff() and ilogbl() return x's exponent, in integer format.
     ilogb(±infinity) returns INT_MAX, ilogb(±NaN) returns FP_ILOGBNAN and
     iillooggbb(0) returns FP_ILOGB0.

